  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a wok or large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and diced chili peppers, sauté for about 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Fold in pine nuts and stir-fry for another minute.",
    "Mix together coconut milk and palm sugar. Pour the mixture into the wok and let it come to a simmer.",
    "Stir occasionally for 5-7 minutes until the liquid is mostly absorbed and the sauce is slightly thickened.",
    "Garnish with finely chopped green onion whites before serving."
